  
  Individual Alerts / Maildrop Alerts

  These options allow you to select the alert length and volume for
  individual and maildrop messages.

        Loud     - loudest volume
        Soft     - softest volume
        Long     - 12 second alert
        Short    - 2 second alert
        Escalert - 2 seconds at softest volume, 2 seconds at 
                   middle volume, 8 seconds at loudest volume
